# Note: This file contains common variables and setup.
# Individual test files will reference these variables.
# 
# Usage:
# 1. Start the API server: dotnet run
# 2. Run authentication tests first to get tokens
# 3. Use the tokens in subsequent tests
# 4. Update @accessToken and @refreshToken variables after successful login
#
# Test Files Structure:
# - api-tests-auth.http (Authentication endpoints)
# - api-tests-users.http (User management)
# - api-tests-dashboard.http (Dashboard and statistics)
# - api-tests-radius.http (RADIUS operations)
# - api-tests-audit.http (Audit logs)
